          "heading": "Validate Location Demand Before Buying Machines",
          "body": {
            "version": 1,
            "nodes": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "Operators should validate location demand before buying machines. New vending operators should prioritize understanding their market. The strongest signals for high location demand include significant foot traffic, the average dwell time of people in the location, and an assessment of existing food and beverage options already available."
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
